chunk_html:
Gymshark Apex Seamless Tank - Papaya Orange/Onyx Grey - Large

WHEN YOU PUT IN THE OVERTIME, APEX STEPS UP EVERY TIME.


Intense training requires durable, reliable performance wear. That's why Apex is designed with strategically placed heat-mapping zones to keep you cool and dry throughout your training.


But don't just take our word for it; rely on technology you can actually see. The ventilation holes on each Apex piece are visible, and each one is a specific size engineered to match where you heat up the most. Each piece in the collection works in harmony, so you can layer your Apex look and always experience premium breathability.


The engineered heat-mapping of Apex means that you're free to focus on your best performance yet - no distractions, no exceptions. Because when you put in the overtime, Apex steps up every time.


- Slim fit
- Seamless construction
- Visible heat and sweat mapping ventilation
- Lightweight material
- Breathable fabric
- Sweat-wicking
- Gymshark logo to chest
- Gymshark heat seal logo to back
- Jacquard Gymshark to internal neck.
- 82% Nylon, 18% Polyester
- We've cut down our use of swing tags, so this product comes without one
- Model is 5'10" and wears size M
- SKU: A1A8S-OBFJ

Men

chunk_html:
Gymshark Whitney Eyelash Knit Bandeau - Cement Brown - Small

GYMSHARK X WHITNEY SIMMONS: THE FINAL COLLECTION


Over the past four collections, we’ve all been on a journey of growth and change alongside Whitney. Now, her fifth and final collection showcases just how far we’ve all come. We can’t wait to see where our journey takes us in the future. The Gymshark x Whitney Simmons collection is back with its famous buttery, supple fabric and a few new ultra soft true knit additions to make every rest day your cosiest. Shaping, resting or reflecting, this collection is here to help you feel beautiful every step of your journey. Embrace your journey and continue to shape the you of tomorrow in the fifth and final Gymshark x Whitney Simmons collection.

Care instructions: Gentle wash inside out with similar colours at 30ºC max. Don't dry clean, bleach, tumble dry or iron. Dry flat.




- Light support bandeau
- New ultra soft true knit material, perfect for rest day
- Subtle branding for a sleek, stylish finish
- Straps are embossed with Gymshark x Whitney Simmons
- Gymshark x Whitney Simmons woven tab branding to centre back hem
- 96% Nylon, 4% Elastane
- We’ve cut down on our use of swing tags, so this product comes without one.
- Model is 5'9" and wears size S
- Video model is 5'10" and wears size XS
- SKU: B4A4Z-NBH2
